translated: Klette, Gustav Gerhard Alfred, district fiscal, Kalmar, born 20/7/97 in Viis-sefjärda, Kalmar 1. Married on the 28th of [month not mentioned] to Rut Astrid Viktoria Verner. Children: Hans, born in 1930. Completed high school in Kalmar in 1917, studied at Schartaus' Trade Institute in Stockholm from 1919 to 1920, appointed as district fiscal in Kalmar in 1925. Transferred to Tunaiän district in 1937, current position as district fiscal in Vässmolösa district since 1946.
